  MDP5001_320_5D7E181C for it — confirmed empirically 2026-07-14: injected
  A369A904 defs were silently replaced by 5D7E181C throughout the .tsproj the
  moment TwinCAT loaded and re-saved the project. The definitions below are
  copied verbatim from THAT TwinCAT-generated output (the live Shark.tsproj
  after a load+save), not from the reference project. The 182C60D3 device-level
  type (WcState/InfoData) is revision-independent and matches both projects.

